# DO commit these so first deploy is instant:
#   data/edubot.db        (seeded knowledge base)
#   models/*.pkl          (trained classifier + vectoriser)
#   models/model_info.txt
# Render free tier has ephemeral disk; without these, every cold
# start would have to retrain. Keeping them in git makes the bot
# snappy from the first request after a deploy. If a local retrain
# changes them, commit the refreshed binaries explicitly.
